            <div type="commentary">
                <ab>Dipinto of a ship. The drawing is very damaged by a large lacuna in the plaster toward the center and in the upper half. What is extant is a very schematic rendering of a rounded hull, with a rockered keel, of which it is difficult to discern the stern from the prow.</ab>
